Hi, we’ve tried to download the “photon vision” software, and then we realized that we don’t need this, and just need to open the dashboard from google.
And now we have a question, Is it possible to use the Limelight camera with the “April Tag” in “Photon vision”?

If you’re talking about the “demo” found on PhotonVison’s website, that won’t interface with your hardware Limelight at all.

Yes, PhotonVision is compatible with Limelight hardware. To actually use the software on your Limelight, PhotonVision has a tutorial about how to flash your Limelight with its software for use with April Tags.

The documentation says for a limelight to use the gloworm image. The latest gloworm image was built off of photonvision-beta-5. We wanted to use beta 6 to use the latest tags…so we built our own. Is there a beta 6 build for limelight? We couldn’t find it, but would love to know for the future.
